OL,7,FJohn Torode's contract on MasterChef
OL,8,Fwill not be renewed after an
OL,9,Faccusation he used an "extremely
OL,10,Foffensive" racist term, the BBC and
OL,11,Fproduction company Banijay UK said.
OL,13,FTorode confirmed on Monday night that
OL,14,Fhe was the subject of an allegation of
OL,15,Fusing racist language that was upheld
OL,16,Fas part of a review into the behaviour
OL,17,Fof his co-presenter Gregg Wallace.
