OL,7,FThe report, commissioned by MasterChef
OL,8,Fproduction company Banijay and led by
OL,9,Flaw firm Lewis Silkin, found 45 out of
OL,10,F83 allegations against Wallace were
OL,11,Fsubstantiated, alongside two
OL,12,Fstandalone allegations made against
OL,13,Fother people, including one for using
OL,14,Fracist language.
OL,16,FIn a post on Instagram, Torode
OL,17,Fconfirmed he was the person alleged to
OL,18,Fhave used racist language but said he
OL,19,Fhad "no recollection of the incident"
OL,20,Fand was "shocked and saddened" by the
OL,21,Fallegation.
